rows.name: Pan Pacific Manila
rows.description: Pan Pacific Manila located approximately 100 metres away from Roxas Boulevard and Manila Bay, and is in the popular Malate entertainment district. It is just a few minutes taxi ride away from many tourist destinations such as Rizal Park, Intramuros and Fort Santiago. The hotel is designed to offer comfortable accommodation to business travellers. It has 236 rooms spread across 21 floors, and 7 function rooms and offers all guests a "butler service". The Pacific Lounge encompasses the top floor of the hotel, with floor-to-ceiling glass walls and offering private meeting room, a separate lounge, a dining area, a bar and a rooftop garden with gazebo. There is an outdoor swimming pool and a gym. Intramuros Golf Course is just a 10-minute drive from the hotel. Come and enjoy the wonderful amenities and impeccable service at Pan Pacific Manila.
rows.address: M. ADRIATICO CORNER GEN. MALVAR STREETS, MALATE,

rows.name: Makati Palace
rows.description: This modern hotel enjoys a strategic setting in the delightful surroundings of Makati. Upon arrival, guests will be instantly impressed by the lavish staircase and the luxurious canopy which adorns the lobby. The hotel is located within easy access of a number of attractions in the area, and lies just a short driving distance away from Ayala Avenue, SM Makrati and Greenbelt shopping centre. This luxurious hotel greets guests with a sophisticated architectural style. The guest rooms are superbly appointed, featuring soothing chocolate tones, with vibrant splashes of colour. The rooms come complete with modern amenities for added comfort and convenience. Guests will be impressed by the excellent facilities that this hotel has to offer.

rows.name: Bayview Park
rows.description: Bayview Park Hotel Manila is located on Roxas Boulevard, directly opposite the US Embassy. It is just a few minutes walk from many popular tourist destinations such as Bay Walk , Rizal Park, Intramuros and the National Library. This city hotel was built in 1994 and renovated in 2007, and is just minutes away from many popular tourist attractions. It has established a reputation as being one of the best value-for-money hotels in Manila. There is a total of 283 superior rooms and suites available, spread over 15 floors. There is an outdoor swimming pool on the hotel grounds, as well as a sauna and a gym. Intramuros Golf Course is not far from the hotel. Guests can dine at the Coffee Shop where a daily buffet and à la carte meals are served. Guests can be assured of a pleasant stay with excellent service when choosing Bayview Park Hotel Manila.
rows.address: ROXAS BOULEVARD, COR. UNITED NATIONS AVE.,1118

rows.name: Palm Grove Hotel formerly known Palm Plaza Hotel
rows.description: This comfortable hotel boasts a great location in Manila’s city centre both for business and leisure travellers alike, as it is situated right in front of Robinson's Place Manila shopping mall and a short walk from Pedro Gil - LRT Station. This accommodation is also just 3 minutes on foot from Manila Bay and a 10-minute walk from US Embassy. Both Manila domestic and international airports are within a 20-minute ride away. Those who stay at this property will be able to choose among three different room types, all of them fully equipped with useful amenities to ensure a truly memorable stay. They are luminous and spacious and decorated in a modern and cosy style. Moreover, during their stay visitors will be able to taste delicious specialities at the on-site restaurant and if they wish to, they can hold private or business events on-site.
rows.address: Pedro Gil Corner M. Adriatico Street, Malate,524

rows.name: Diamond Hotel Philippines
rows.description: Situated in Manila's Ermita-Malate neighbourhood, the hotel is close to Baywalk, SM Mall of Asia and Rizal Park. Guests can choose from the hotel's 9 impressive and fully-equipped function rooms suitable for every event (business or party). Further facilities at the hotel include a lobby with lift access, a restaurant, and room and laundry services. The guest rooms are equipped with TVs with satellite channels, wired high-speed Internet access and in-room safes. All units feature coffee and tea makers and complimentary bottled water. The en suite bathrooms offer showers, bathrobes and hairdryers. Guests are invited to take a rejuvenating plunge in the outdoor swimming pool and hot tub. Dubbed as the most authentic Japanese restaurant in Manila, the hotel's award-winning restaurant indulges guests in exquisite Japanese food masterfully prepared by a Japanese chef.
rows.address: Roxas Boulevard cor. Dr. J. Quintos St.,. 0 .

rows.name: Crown Regency Hotel - Makati
rows.description: The hotel enjoys a strategic location in Makati, one of the leading business, entertainment, and commercial hub of the Philippines. The domestic and international airports are both just minutes away.  The hotel combines convenience and comfort, ensuring unmatched hotel satisfaction. It has a lobby, a currency exchange and conference facilities. Further amenities include a bar and a restaurant. Room and laundry services are also available. Each hotel room comes fully furnished with standard amenities, including a well-appointed kitchen and a bathroom with full bath facilities. The rooms also feature a tasteful living space, as well as an elegant dining area adjoining the kitchen. The hotel features a gym facility, where guests can power up and rejuvenate with the help of cardio machines and body toning/strengthening equipment.
rows.address: A. Arnaiz Avenue, San Lorenzo Village,1026

rows.name: Atrium Hotel
rows.description: The hotel is located in the Makati City business district of Manila. Bars, nightlife and shopping opportunities can all be found in the vicinity. Baclaran Church, Manila Ocean Park, Rizal Park - Intramuros and the SM Mall of Asia are all easily accessible by car or public transport. The bus and train stations are both about a 10-minute walk away. The hotel is located a 10-15 minutes' drive away from the Airport. The hotel also offers a massage treatment service. Breakfast is served as a buffet, while lunch is served à la carte. This hotel is the perfect base for business and sightseeing in Manila.
rows.address: 15F TAFT CENTRALE EXCHANGE GIL PUYAT COR.TAFT AVE.,

rows.name: Paseo Premiere Hotel
rows.description: Strategically located in the heart of Santa Rosa Business Park, this 4-star property is across from Laguna Techno Park, one of the largest export zones in Calabarzon. Each room at this property boasts its modern style furnishing to meet the needs of all guests. Within the premises, guests will find a casino, room service, meeting facilities on-site, and a fully equipped gym for complete enjoyment. In addition to all the luxurious amenities, business travelers are offered in-room technology that includes high-speed broadband internet access and data ports. Within easy walking distance, guests will find Paseo de Santa Rosa Mall. Each room at this property enjoys magnificent views of Santa Rosa and the mountain scenery of Tagaytay and Laguna Lake. Enjoy the simple luxury, relaxing ambiance, and personalized services of Paseo Premiere Hotel.

rows.name: Hotel Jen Manila
rows.description: The hotel on Roxas Boulevard is just 400 metres from Manila's conference and exhibition centres and 20-minutes' drive from Ninoy Aquino International Airport. Its rooms offer LCD TVs and views of Manila Bay and Roxas Boulevard. The hotel provides guests with recreational facilities such as the Paseo del Sol outdoor swimming pool, children's wading pool, and a fitness centre. The hotel also offers in-room massage. The signature restaurant serves authentic Japanese cuisine and houses a cozy bar. Asian cuisine and an international lunch buffet is served at another on-site restaurant. The bar at the lobby offers nightly entertainment, while the hotel's cyber offers light fare and broadband Internet access.
